                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       class="tour-categories__item">
                                    Экскурсионный </a><a data-v-38205e9e="" href="https://youtravel.me/tours/type/%D0%B4%D0%B6%D0%B8%D0%BF_%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D1%8B" target="_blank" class="tour-categories__item"> На внедорожниках </a></div>
